name: Camacho - Blackout - Robusto
additionalNotes: Camacho Blackout is a limited edition cigar released by Davidoff in 2013 with a 2006 vintage Honduran wrapper from the top priming of the tobacco plant, an aged Nicaraguan binder from 2009, and aged fillers from Honduras (2003), Nicaragua (2008) and Brazil (2009).  The tobacco for the wrapper has been press-fermented for a very dark. oily result. Only 5,000 boxes of 20 cigars produced.
